review: Whenever it comes to dental treatment could be any kind one always gets freaked out due to the pain one has to undergo, I was one of them having sensitivity in one if my molar tooth ,Dr did my x-ray of that particular tooth and found having crack but luckily it was not that deep so it was suggested for Root canal treatment, it took me some while to prepare my self but Dr assured me dnt worry about the pain and within an hour it was done , I was relaxed and pain free. There moto is Invest in your Smile and I just did it,tha k you Dr Shipra and the team.
